# Repo Structure and Exports Registration

When adding or reorganizing folders that rely on barrel exports, keep structure and export registration in sync.

## Required workflow

- Keep feature code grouped by route/domain (for example: `src/app/(task)`).
- If a folder is expected to have an auto-generated `index.ts`, register that folder in `EXPORT_CONFIGS` inside `scripts/generate-exports.ts`.
- Run `bun run exports-gen` after adding a new registered folder or moving files between registered folders.
- Do not manually maintain generated barrel files if they are marked auto-generated.

## Reference example

Current registered folders include:

- `src/ui`
- `src/app/(task)/components`

These are configured in `scripts/generate-exports.ts` under `EXPORT_CONFIGS`.

## Change checklist

- [ ] New folder location is added to `EXPORT_CONFIGS` when needed.
- [ ] Exports are regenerated.
- [ ] Imports in affected files are updated to use the new barrel path.
